'''Bori''' is a [[Tani languages|Tani]] language of [[India]]. Bori is spoken in Payum Circle, [[West Siang District]], [[Arunachal Pradesh]] (Megu 1988).
Bori is spoken by the [[Bori people|Bori]] people, an indigenous tribe of India.
