'''Nkutu''' (Nkuchu, Kitkutshu) is a [[Bantu languages|Bantu]] language of northern [[Kasai-Oriental]] Province, [[Democratic Republic of the Congo]]. It is a member of the [[Tetela languages|Tetela]] group of Bantu languages.
